Package: bayeslincom
Type: Package
Title: Linear Combinations of Bayesian Posterior Samples
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Josue E.", "Rodriguez", email = "josue.rodriguez594@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Donald", "Williams", email = "drwwilliams@ucdavis.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Computes point estimates, standard deviations, and credible intervals for 
             linear combinations of posterior samples. Optionally performs ROPE tests.
             References: Kruschke and Liddell (2018) <doi:10.3758/s13423-016-1221-4>; 
             Rouder, Haaf, and Vandekerckhove (2018) <doi:10.3758/s13423-017-1420-7>.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
